OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FTransport for London (TfL) has been
OL,8,Furged to reconsider its approach to
OL,9,Fstaffing Tube stations because of
OL,10,Fconcerns over fare dodgers.
OL,12,FThe London Assembly Transport
OL,13,FCommittee wrote to the transport body
OL,14,Fcalling on it to reassess its
OL,15,F"routine" use of lone working without
OL,16,Fmitigation to improve the "reality and
OL,17,Fperception" of staff safety in the
OL,18,Fcontext of fare evasion.
