OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FThe committee heard evidence from the
OL,8,FRail, Maritime and Transport union
OL,9,F(RMT) that staff working on their own
OL,10,Fat stations feel less confident to
OL,11,Fintervene when they see a fare dodger
OL,12,Fbecause of the fear of physical
OL,13,Fviolence.
OL,15,FLondon Assembly member Elly Baker, who
OL,16,Fchairs the committee, said: "Fare
OL,17,Fevasion is unacceptable ` causing TfL
OL,18,Ffinancial losses that eventually
OL,19,Fbecome the expense of the vast
OL,20,Fmajority who pay their fares.
OL,26,@xD@]OU
