OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,F"All too often, fare evasion is also
OL,8,Flinked to violence and aggression
OL,9,Ftowards TfL frontline staff who feel
OL,10,Fthis issue is getting worse.
OL,12,F"TfL must ensure more is done to
OL,13,Fensure gatelines are in operation and
OL,14,Fstaffed at all stations and reduce the
OL,15,Famount of times staff are being asked
OL,16,Fto work on their own on our transport
OL,17,Fnetwork."
