OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,8,Fcalled on TfL to "end lone working"
OL,9,Fand "increase staffing across the
OL,10,Fnetwork".
OL,12,FHe went on: "Tackling fare evasion is
OL,13,Fthe biggest trigger for staff
OL,14,Fassaults, and we welcome the London
OL,15,FAssembly Transport Committee's call
OL,16,Ffor more frontline resources and real
OL,17,Fconsequences for those who attack our
OL,18,Fmembers at work.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@cO]qD@EOUrD@HO]tD@MOU
