OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,F"Our recent survey shows that 60% of
OL,8,Frail staff who have been assaulted
OL,9,Fwere working alone at the time. That
OL,10,Fis simply unacceptable."
OL,12,FTfL figures show 3.5% of passengers
OL,13,Facross its network evade fares,
OL,14,Fcosting it #130 million annually.
OL,16,FIn May, shadow justice secretary
OL,17,FRobert Jenrick posted a widely-viewed
OL,18,Fvideo on social media in which he
OL,19,Fconfronted people who forced their way
OL,20,Fthrough the ticket barriers at
OL,21,FStratford station in east London.
