OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FA TfL spokesperson said: "Fare evasion
OL,8,Fis a criminal offence and robs
OL,9,FLondoners of investment in safe, clean
OL,10,Fand reliable public transport.
OL,12,F"That's why we are strengthening our
OL,13,Fcapability to deter and detect fare
OL,14,Fevaders, including expanding our team
OL,15,Fof professional investigators and
OL,16,Fusing the latest technology to target
OL,17,Fthe most prolific fare evaders across
OL,18,Fthe network.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUtD@AOU
