OL,3,CTfL urged to reconsider lone working
OL,4,Cat Tube stations over fare evasion
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,F"The current fare evasion rate is
OL,8,Fsignificantly lower than many cities
OL,9,Fglobally, including New York's 9%, and
OL,10,Fthe same rate in London would equate
OL,11,Fto more than #400 million of lost
OL,12,Frevenue per year.
OL,14,F"Our data-driven strategy to tackle
OL,15,Ffare evasion is already making an
OL,16,Fimpact, with the pan-TfL fare evasion
OL,17,Frate dropping to 3.5% from 3.8% in
OL,18,F2023/24.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
